|-
| [[Data Types#Standard data types|Byte]]
| The range of the shake randomness.
|-
| [[Data Types#Standard data types|Byte]]
| The amplitude (maximum displacement from 0) of the shake.
|-
| [[Data Types#Standard data types|Byte]]
| The phase (where in its cycle the oscillation is at t = 0) of the shake.
|-
